07-4596-81cd-d377f3f44790--2017-0307_kalimotxo-joy-the-baker_julia-gartland-132.jpg, https://images.food52.com/RBkOrlf9WXmgLITUm7hkqn3i5aw=/750x500/a08d6801-2107-4596-81cd-d377f3f44790--2017-0307_kalimotxo-joy-the-baker_julia-gartland-132.jpg 2x\" alt=\"Kalimotxo in glasses\" width=\"1348\" height=\"898\" data-pin-media=\"https://images.food52.com/dPv8oqoE_dqCFbMGFSeMV7s3hUs=/2000x2000/a08d6801-2107-4596-81cd-d377f3f44790--2017-0307_kalimotxo-joy-the-baker_julia-gartland-132.jpg\" data-pin-url=\"https://food52.com/blog/28638-what-is-kalimotxo-easy-cocktails\" data-pin-description=\"The Perfect Party Drink is Only Two Ingredients on Food52\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/-PqvKTejqJ38SNU3d4NhT8nhimk=/375x250/a08d6801-2107-4596-81cd-d377f3f44790--2017-0307_kalimotxo-joy-the-baker_julia-gartland-132.jpg, https://images.food52.com/RBkOrlf9WXmgLITUm7hkqn3i5aw=/750x500/a08d6801-2107-4596-81cd-d377f3f44790--2017-0307_kalimotxo-joy-the-baker_julia-gartland-132.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://images.food52.com/dPv8oqoE_dqCFbMGFSeMV7s3hUs=/2000x2000/a08d6801-2107-4596-81cd-d377f3f44790--2017-0307_kalimotxo-joy-the-baker_julia-gartland-132.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n      \u003c/div\u003e\n\n      \u003cp\u003e\u003cspan\u003ePhoto by Julia Gartland \u003c/span\u003e\n      \u003c/p\u003e\n    \u003c/section\u003e\n\n\n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n          \u003cdiv\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eFirst things first: For the uninitiated, a kalimotxo is equal parts red wine and cola served over ice, often with a squeeze of lemon or lime juice. It’s a Spanish drink, a classic from the Basque Country but enjoyed all over. It’s also a party drink: light, sweet, and with a pleasantly low ABV. I’m a recent adopter, relatively speaking, but it didn’t take much for me to become an evangelist for this unlikely combination.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eLately I’ve been obsessed with the idea of having a “\u003ca href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@aroundeight/video/7415593069162155295\" target=\"_blank\"\u003ehouse beverage\u003c/a\u003e,” a hosting concept introduced to me by \u003ca href=\"https://www.tiktok.com/@aroundeight\" target=\"_blank\"\u003e@aroundeight\u003c/a\u003e on TikTok. The idea is: If you want to be the kind of person that can host an impromptu dinner party, you should always have makings of a drink that can also be served at a moment\u0026#39;s notice.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n\n  \u003cdiv id=\"productCollectionRoot\"\u003e\n      \u003cp\u003eFrom Our Shop\u003c/p\u003e\n\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\n  \u003ca data-sku-id=\"45092\" data-vendor-id=\"966\" data-vendor-name=\"Craighill \" data-category-name=\"Barware\" data-in-stock=\"true\" data-price=\"168.0\" data-ga-grid-item=\"slide: 1\" data-product-id=\"13381\" data-product-name=\"Craighill x East Fork Cocktail Set\" data-url=\"/shop/products/13381-craighill-east-fork-stainless-steel-cocktail-set\" data-img=\"https://images.food52.com/OzLWG7tFzzpJqnyDBkFHyKQrrik=/520x520/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg\" data-price-range=\"$168\" data-ga-event=\"gridInteraction\" data-ga-event-action=\"From Our Shop\" data-ga-event-label=\"none\" data-ga-destination-url=\"/shop/products/13381-craighill-east-fork-stainless-steel-cocktail-set\" href=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/13381-craighill-east-fork-stainless-steel-cocktail-set\"\u003e\n    \u003cdiv\u003e\u003cpicture\u003e\u003csource srcset=\"data:image/gif;base64,R0lGODlhAQABAAAAACH5BAEKAAEALAAAAAABAAEAAAICTAEAOw==\" type=\"image/webp\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/IwX3tdP5hXZGjN6xGzM9rpxVF6w=/520x520/filters:format(webp)/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg, https://images.food52.com/eX58IXC84OETd2bErmvYpXUhvbY=/1040x1040/filters:format(webp)/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg 2x\"/\u003e\u003cimg srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/OzLWG7tFzzpJqnyDBkFHyKQrrik=/520x520/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg, https://images.food52.com/jPOZ2cR_2pXPYvi3zptOByiE83A=/1040x1040/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg 2x\" alt=\"Craighill x East Fork Cocktail Set\" width=\"520\" height=\"520\" data-pin-media=\"https://images.food52.com/jPOZ2cR_2pXPYvi3zptOByiE83A=/1040x1040/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg\" data-pin-url=\"https://food52.com/shop/products/13381-craighill-east-fork-stainless-steel-cocktail-set\" data-pin-description=\"Craighill x East Fork Cocktail Seton Food52\" data-srcset=\"https://images.food52.com/OzLWG7tFzzpJqnyDBkFHyKQrrik=/520x520/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg, https://images.food52.com/jPOZ2cR_2pXPYvi3zptOByiE83A=/1040x1040/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg 2x\" src=\"https://images.food52.com/jPOZ2cR_2pXPYvi3zptOByiE83A=/1040x1040/a443b34f-1772-47bb-a48e-0e830f947c1d--2024-1023_craighill_mescola-cocktail-set_stainless-steel_mid_emailsite_1x1_GIF_mj-kroeger-321.jpg\"/\u003e\u003c/picture\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n    \u003c/a\u003e\n\n    \n\u003c/div\u003e\n  \u003c/div\u003e\n\n              \u003cp\u003eIn choosing a house beverage, as she lays out in the video, you want something relatively easy and inexpensive. It also needs to strike a balance between being unique to you and your home while also being enjoyable and accessible to the wide range of people you may plan on hosting one day.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eThis concept struck me, but for a while it was looking like I’d have to settle for keeping a stash of Miller High Life in the fridge. I do always have the stuff to crank out a decent old fashioned, but I’m not sure that fits the bill for most guests.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n\n\n              \u003cp\u003eHowever, when I first tasted the kalimotxo in recipe development, I knew that I had struck gold. It’s easy to love, and I know that if my guests haven’t heard of it, they are in for a pleasant surprise. The trick is to pick a very dry red wine, like a Spanish rioja—it doesn’t need to be expensive. This comes into perfect balance with the sugary sweet soda, while the (optional) squeeze of citrus gives the drink a little lift.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \u003cp\u003eYou already know how to make it, but we have a \u003ca href=\"https://food52.com/recipes/69166-joy-the-baker-s-kalimotxo\"\u003erecipe\u003c/a\u003e if you need a refresher. Try it yourself and go spread the good word—maybe at your next dinner party.\u003c/p\u003e\n              \n  \n\n\n\n              \u003chr/\u003e\n\n              \n              \u003ccenter\u003e\n\u003cem\u003eWhat’s your house beverage? Let us know in the comments\u003c/em\u003e\n\u003c/center\u003e\n          \u003c/div\u003e\n\n            \n\n\n            \n            \n\n\n\n            \n\u003cdiv\u003e\n  \n\n    \u003cp\u003e\n      Test Kitchen Content Creator at Food52\n    \u003c/p\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\n        \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n  \u003cdiv\u003e\n      \u003ch3\u003ePopular on Food52\u003c/h3\u003e\n      \n    \u003c/div\u003e\n\n  \n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e",
